{
  "stem": "11672.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Don't get you to eat too much, and you work so hard.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You take that stones, marble, from the mine, and I have with other five boys from Poland-- they take this five kilometers to the other station, to push this.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] There, I stayed in this place maybe [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] three month.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1940.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And from this place [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] take me to a town [PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] called Melitopol.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So that city, maybe there's 60,000, 70,000 people in the city lived.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This is-- but the [INAUDIBLE] with cream, like here, Florida.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Warm, beautiful there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there I start [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to work like a tailor, like a furrier, you know?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My professional-- Had you learned this from your father?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this is a shop in the government-- everything belonged there to the government-- used especially for the city hall.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[SIGHS] And I remember [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I didn't get letters from my parents.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I thought that my parents not even know where I am.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I went to the post office, and I'm lucky I find there a Polish Russian worker.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She work in the post office.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She tell me, you know what?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In two months, maybe six weeks, you can send letters to Poland.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Well, the Russians with Germany maked a pact, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know what means?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "An arrangement.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I sent letters to my parents and I get back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And I sent them-- my mother and my father asked me for satin and for a little [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] flour to make breads or something, you know?",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I sent them-- somebody try and send it to me-- you know, I sent them.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
